room_title: Escape room "North Pole Melt Down" by Psychopath Escape Room in Fayetteville (WV)
room_description: Oh no! You didn't make the Nice List this year. Don't worry, Buddy the Elf believes you deserve a second chance! He is giving you access to the North Pole where Santa hides the Lists.  While Santa is out on his final test run, you must find the Nice List to save Christmas. You only have 60 minutes before Santa returns!
